(Product Requirements Document: Keywize) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#1. Product name) Tj
T*
(Keywize) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#2. One-line pitch) Tj
T*
(Locked out? Call once. Keywize calls locksmiths, compares real all-in prices, negotiates) Tj
T*
(under your budget, and protects you from bait-and-switch scams.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#3. Problem) Tj
T*
(People who are locked out or have lost keys are stressed and usually call the first) Tj
T*
(locksmith they find. Locksmith pricing is often unclear. A phone quote may start at $39,) Tj
T*
(but the final bill can become $250 or more after dispatch fees, labor, drilling, parts,) Tj
T*
(after-hours fees, and tax. Customers do not know which services they actually need, and) Tj
T*
(they do not know which questions to ask.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#4. Target users) Tj
T*
(- Renters locked out of an apartment or room) Tj
T*
(- Students in dorms or shared housing) Tj
T*
(- Roommates who need new keys) Tj
T*
(- Tenants whose keys were stolen) Tj
T*
(- People with a broken key stuck inside the lock) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#5. Supported MVP cases) Tj
T*
(1. Room door key lost) Tj
T*
(2. Key inside room and locked out) Tj
T*
(3. Main apartment key lost) Tj
T*
(4. Key stolen) Tj
T*
(5. Broken key inside lock) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#6. Core promise) Tj
T*
(Keywize will:) Tj
T*
(- Understand the user's lock problem through voice or web intake) Tj
T*
(- Ask for max budget and urgency) Tj
T*
(- Confirm the user is authorized to request locksmith service) Tj
T*
(- Call at least 3 locksmiths or simulated locksmiths) Tj
T*
(- Ask protective anti-scam questions) Tj
T*
(- Capture itemized quotes in a structured format) Tj
T*
(- Use real competing quotes to negotiate price or terms) Tj
T*
(- Rank vendors by price, ETA, risk, and evidence) Tj
T*
(- Recommend the safest best-value option) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#7. Differentiation) Tj
T*
(This is not a generic quote comparison tool. It is an emergency anti-scam negotiator.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Unique features:) Tj
T*
(- Bait-and-switch risk score) Tj
T*
(- No-drill-first verification) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
