stream
BT
/F1 10 Tf
14 TL
50 760 Td
(Start with 0 risk points. Add points:) Tj
T*
(- Says "starts at" without giving total: +35) Tj
T*
(- Refuses itemized pricing: +25) Tj
T*
(- Refuses to confirm dispatch fee: +20) Tj
T*
(- Mentions drilling before diagnosis: +25) Tj
T*
(- Refuses company name or invoice name: +20) Tj
T*
(- Does not require proof of residence: +15) Tj
T*
(- Quote is more than 40 percent below median: +20) Tj
T*
(- Quote is more than 50 percent above median: +10) Tj
T*
(- Cannot provide ETA: +10) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Risk levels:) Tj
T*
(- 0 to 24: Low) Tj
T*
(- 25 to 59: Medium) Tj
T*
(- 60 to 100: High) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#12. Agent behavior rules) Tj
T*
(The agent must:) Tj
T*
(- Never invent a competing quote) Tj
T*
(- Never lie about the job) Tj
T*
(- Never claim the user owns the property unless the user confirmed authorization) Tj
T*
(- Disclose it is an AI if asked) Tj
T*
(- Ask for total all-in price before sharing the user's max budget) Tj
T*
(- End every call with a structured outcome) Tj
T*
(- Push for non-destructive opening first) Tj
T*
(- Ask for confirmation before accepting anything above the user's max price) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#13. Anti-scam call script) Tj
T*
(The caller agent should ask:) Tj
T*
(1. Can you give the total out-the-door estimate including dispatch, labor, parts, after-) Tj
T*
(  hours, tax, and any other fees?) Tj
T*
(2. Is the dispatch fee included in that total?) Tj
T*
(3. Will you attempt non-destructive entry before drilling?) Tj
T*
(4. Under what condition would drilling be required?) Tj
T*
(5. Will the technician call before starting if the price changes?) Tj
T*
(6. What is the ETA?) Tj
T*
(7. Do you require ID or proof of residence before opening?) Tj
T*
(8. What company name will appear on the invoice?) Tj
T*
(9. Are any keys included?) Tj
T*
(10. Is there a warranty?) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#14. MVP success criteria) Tj
T*
(- User can complete web intake) Tj
T*
(- User can enter ideal price and max price) Tj
T*
(- System creates a structured job spec) Tj
T*
(- Demo calls or simulated calls produce 3 structured quotes) Tj
T*
(- At least one vendor changes price or terms because of another real quote) Tj
T*
(- Final report ranks all vendors) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
